hints.description: This company is a leading producer of clean energy, primarily focusing on nuclear generation. They also provide energy solutions and infrastructure to utilities and commercial customers across the United States. Notably, they are a significant player in the transition to a low-carbon economy and are expanding into renewable energy sources like solar and wind.
hints.funFact1: The current CEO, **** *******, previously served as the CEO of Baltimore Gas and Electric, a subsidiary of the company, demonstrating a long history within the organization.
hints.funFact2: In 2018, the company acquired *** ********, a major provider of energy storage solutions, signaling a strategic move to enhance grid reliability and integrate renewable energy more effectively.
